				Mine syncs neatly with your Facebook Timeline.
			</div>
			
			<div class="square text light last">
				Flick a switch to post favorites as large photos.
			</div>
			<div class="rectangle last">
				<%=image_tag 'home_mine/intro/intro3.jpg'%>
			</div>	
					
		</div> <!-- /squares -->
	</div>	
</div> <!-- /steps -->



